data.description: INVESTOR OPPORTUNITY! 3 blocks from The Roads, 2 blocks from Calle Ocho and only minutes from Brickell,  this 5,000 SF property is a one-of-a-kind estate-sale with multiple opportunities for smart buyers. The 3-bedroom 1.5 bath home with den may be purchased for owner occupancy or leased with spacious front and back porches. The covered carport connects to the home and the detached storage/laundry room is equipped with electrical, water, and plumbing. UNIQUE BONUS for investors: property is fully and legally zoned for duplex conversion or new development for up to two dwellings in a semi-detached (side-by-side) or 2-story (upstairs/downstairs) layout. On-street parking is separated from main road, perfect for multiple owners or visiting guests. Unbeatable location. EASY TO SHOW.
